Name: HardView
Version: 1.1.2
Summary: A Python library for collecting hardware information (BIOS, System, CPU, RAM, Disk, Network).
Home-page: https://github.com/gafoo173/HardView
Author: gafoo
Author-email: omarwaled3374@gmail.com
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3
Classifier: License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License
Classifier: Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows
Classifier: Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux
Classifier: Topic :: System :: Hardware
Classifier: Development Status :: 3 - Alpha

A comprehensive Python library for querying low-level hardware information on Windows and Linux, including BIOS, system, CPU, RAM, disk drives, and network adapters. Data is returned in JSON format.
